# Lessons

## List Lessons

```shell
curl -u "DOMAIN:API_KEY" "https://api.lesson.ly/api/v1/lessons"
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```json
{
  "type": "lessons",
  "lessons":[
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "First Lesson"
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Second Lesson"
      },
    ]
}
```

This endpoint retrieves all lessons.

### HTTP Request

`GET https://api.lesson.ly/api/v1/lessons`

